Package vstore.framework.logging.log_events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LogCancelLoggingEvent  
    LogDownloadDoneEvent
    This event gets published by the Downloader, if a download is done.
    LogDownloadStartEvent
    This event gets published by the Downloader if a new download has been started.
    LogMatchingAddNodeEvent
    Adds the decided node to the logger for a file decision.
    LogMatchingAddRuleEvent
    This event gets published, if the decision used a rule for matching.
    LogMatchingDoneEvent
    This event acts as an alternative for LogUploadDoneEvent, since this will not get published, if the file is only stored on the phone.
    LogMatchingStartLoggingEvent
    This event should be published, if the Logger should start logging for a new matching.
    LogUploadDoneEvent
    This event gets published if a file has finished uploading.
